title: Hour 1 - Lakers, Browns and Ryen Russillo
itunes:title: Hour 1 - Lakers, Browns and Ryen Russillo
description:
In hour 1 of the show, Colin pose the question concerning the courage of the Lakers and if they would trade Anthony Davis for Kyrie Irving. The Browns clearly had no plan for Baker Mayfield and is now feeling it. Ryan Russillo joins to talk his affinity for Steph Curry, the Celtics and more.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
